{"tid":901790,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"全港得16間男校英中，但有32間女校英中","createTime":"2018-11-14T09:31:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T12:44:37.000Z","uid":23141,"like":83,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"90497c3e99a4f3adf7c8ba0857fbcc7c736d5821","tid":901790,"uid":23141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T09:31:26.000Z","msg":"以上包哂直資、資助、官立<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.schooland.hk/ss/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.schooland.hk%2Fss%2F&d=wzPql2HN1U%2FdtEo8BWkm%2BS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=3a60a058\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.schooland.hk/ss/</a><br />\n呢個網filter 嘅數據，唔知準唔準<br />\n男校英中：2間官立、4間直資、10間資助<br />\n女校英中：1間官立、5間直資、26間資助<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n都未計男女校入面女生肯定多啲<br />\n因為跟成績派，退一萬步，當男女遲熟早熟真係無分別，以前跟性別派位唔公平，打死無怨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但點解女校英中多男校英中一倍<br />\n係咪英中好明顯影響前途/入大學機會<br />\n咁樣有無性別歧視，同平機會投訴？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n繼續咁分男校、女校有無必要<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20940cc642403064ed0db48635f849d252cdc92e","tid":901790,"uid":73,"like":9,"dislike":26,"score":-17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T09:33:58.000Z","msg":"咁睇我間學校都唔係太差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申: 觀瑪"},{"pid":"b264b1ccc768ef29bb3535726269ceb3f723debb","tid":901790,"uid":9315,"like":3,"dislike":19,"score":-16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T09:41:31.000Z","msg":"連登仔好似仲停留係爭論英文究竟有冇用 &amp; 讀大學究竟有冇用既層次wor<br />\n<br />\n冇英中讀求之不得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72f78fcd425cb8c8481b474981fcd1e286829c92","tid":901790,"uid":23141,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T09:42:07.000Z","msg":"呢啲學校受政府資助，帶頭玩歧視？"},{"pid":"ef18f7627964aa4de02d7c7bc714a48b77ec41bc","tid":901790,"uid":23141,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"b264b1ccc768ef29bb3535726269ceb3f723debb","tid":901790,"uid":9315,"like":3,"dislike":19,"score":-16,"cite